Method Detail

merge

public ClusterTemplate merge(Collection<AbstractTemplate> templates,
                             ClusterTemplate initialTemplate)
                      throws TemplateImmutabilityException,
                             TemplateNotFoundException,
                             TemplateValidationException
Merge all templates in order into new cluster template. At the end we have cluster template with fully merged state from included partials and extended parents.

Parameters:
templates - templates in order to merge into new cluster template. Recommend to use LinkedHashSet or List for saving templates order.
initialTemplate - specified template, last child of templates chain. Name, description, label ans icon will be taken from it for final cluster template.
Returns:
Cluster template with merged state
Throws:
TemplateImmutabilityException - if some template tries to override immutable config
TemplateNotFoundException - if template is unknown type.
TemplateValidationException
